<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Moorooka's buyer pool is genuinely layered. First-home buyers priced out of Annerley and Greenslopes arrive with clear-eyed research: they know the comparison and they understand what extra budget they would need for the northern neighbours. Investors come for yield and the transition story, particularly near the Rocklea and Ipswich Road fringes. Young families want a free-standing home close enough to the CBD to be practical. That mix means a well-run Moorooka campaign reaches multiple competing buyer groups simultaneously, which is where sellers capture the best result.
    </p>
